I had planned to fire my kiln today, and get one more batch of pottery done before this weekend. Instead, a pretty big earthquake (6.4 magnitude) knocked out all the power in Humboldt County. We’re all fine- I know many others fared much worse! Hoping to have some open hours in my shop later this week- will keep you posted. Take care everyone! ❤️
